'''''Maid of Sentiile''''' was one of many [[Starship/Legends|ships]] that crashed into the rogue [[Planet/Legends|planetoid]] [[Tembora]]. [[Gillon]] was one of the crewmembers aboard this ship that were sent on recon duty to the [[Tembora Research Station]]. He was the only person on the ship who managed to survive their encounter with [[KLR-B1]]. It is unknown what happened to this ship, though it can be assumed that it was destroyed by KLR-B1 along with all other ships which landed on the planet.

